<br>
The bridge and ramp leading to the dungeon is filled with monsters that are red and purple to level 50s, so it's not even remotely soloable.<br>
<br>
I recall seeing a post on a message board where someone claimed that a group of 4 50s were able to get in and kill some mobs on the first level, but if that's true at all, it was a group that was very careful and very familiar with each other, most people will probably need to hook up with a 50-80 person minimum raid.<br>
<br>
BTW, for those that have gone farther than me (we only made it to the first key guy on the one raid I was on), do most of the mobs continue to be crush-friendly skeleton and lich types (at least the trash mobs)? <p>Acus TwinHammer<br>
